data.description: A gorgeous home nestled just a short walk away from the picturesque downtown Goodrich Village and the serene Goodrich Mill Pond. This completely remodeled gem boasts updates including a new furnace, windows, roof, electrical, plumbing, and well, all completed in 2015. A privacy fence was added in 2019 to enhance the tranquil setting. Step inside to discover a custom kitchen with granite countertops and cherry cabinets, complemented by stainless steel appliances. Plus, the home also features many smart home features, including smart switches and plugs.  Notably, this property is in a great location for commuting, with short distances to many major towns and cities. Don't miss this turnkey treasure in a prime location, offering both modern convenience and accessibility.
